com.shop.util.generic
Interface GenericIOClient<T>

public interface GenericIOClient<T>

Client/connection abstraction. Use GenericIOFactory to allocate a new connection.

disableHeartbeats

void disableHeartbeats()
By default, GenericIO clients use a heartbeat mechanism to validate server-to-client and client-to-server connections. Calling this method turns this feature off for this connection.

Use this with caution. It stops the client from sending hearbeats and also stops the client from interpreting heartbeats.
